%A7n-Quang-Tri%E1%BB%81u/Quy-chu-t%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-rM7Bzb-lkueQYfzxyjfffg">Quy chu tức sự - 歸舟即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Quang-Tri%E1%BB%81u/author-0-sb0Y9_iaj8YxIytSFQ8A">Trần Quang Triều</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-T%C3%B4ng-M%E1%BA%A1i/Thi%C3%AAn-thu-gi%C3%A1m-ph%C3%BA/poem-aNFJrxFI6pAICUyX7CKLvQ">Thiên thu giám phú - 千秋鑑賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-T%C3%B4ng-M%E1%BA%A1i/author-EY3eHTvDpkwLbISMoUQtYg">Phạm Tông Mại</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Ng%C5%A9-L%C3%A3o/V%C3%A3n-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%E1%BB%91c-c%C3%B4ng-H%C6%B0ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-v%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-kiZh9eDYIvkq5hsDF9vomA">Vãn thượng tướng quốc công Hưng Đạo đại vương - 輓上將國公興道大王</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Ng%C5%A9-L%C3%A3o/author-05pC1bg9XnAmUOwwr3zTLw">Phạm Ngũ Lão</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/V%C3%A3n-t%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BB%93-c%C3%B4ng/poem-cDElVqf2JwRbA8T7Kf-a_A">Vãn tư đồ công - 輓司徒公</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/author-KitWPFSrhqgQGR4JMcSBew">Nguyễn Ức</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
